Entries.Introduction: Oh, hey. So you're the new {{Lowercase: {{Random: {{GenericNoun}} }} }}, huh? I think we're going to get along great. I'm Alex.#$e#I'll see you around.
Entries.Resort_Chair: Aren't you hot in that outfit? You gotta get some ocean breeze goin'!
Entries.Tue: The beach is a cool place to hang out and soak up some rays.#e#You gotta spend some time in the sun or else you'll get all pale.#$e#Hey, do you wanna hang out with me at the beach some time?
Entries.Wed: Looks like a good day to play catch, huh?$u#$e#$q 5/6 Wed_01_old#I'd ask you to throw the ball around, but you don't really seem like the sports type.#$r 6 0 Wed_01_02#I'm fine just watching you from a distance.#$r 5 15 Wed_01_01#I want to play catch with you!#$r 5 0 Wed_01_03#(angry) What's that supposed to mean?
Entries.Fri: Hey, what's up @. Did you get new pants? You're doing something right.#e#Oh, I almost forgot! It's my day for doing push-ups!#e#Every time I do push-ups I try to do one more than last time. Pretty cool strategy, huh?
Entries.event_box3: ...Thanks, @.#$b#You've become my best friend in the whole town... #$b#Is that embarrassing to say?$l
Entries.summer_Mon: Hey, @. You've got a nice tan going.$h#$e#The more I practice this summer, the easier it'll be for me to go pro.#$e#Then you'd be able to say you knew me once. Cool, huh?
Entries.summer_Wed: Hey @, I've got a question for you.#$b#$q 52/53 summer_Wed_01_old#Do you think I'll ever turn pro?#$r 52 30 summer_Wed_01_01#You're destined to be a sports legend#$r 52 0 summer_Wed_01_02#Maybe, if you practice a lot#$r 53 -50 summer_Wed_01_03#No, you'll most likely fail and become a salesman
Entries.summer_Wed_01_03: That's insane. You're just jealous that I'm talented and popular and you're not.$a#$e#Get away from me.$a
Entries.summer_Thu: Hey, you must be getting pretty strong working on that farm all day.#$e#Maybe you'll reach my level some day. Something to look forward to, huh?#$e#Why do you have that look on your face?
Entries.fall_Wed: Hey, can I ask you something?#$e#$q 54/55 fall_Wed_01_old#What do you think about my haircut?#$r 54 30 fall_Wed_01_01#It looks very fashionable.#$r 55 -30 fall_Wed_01_02#It looks like some kind of fungal growth.
